companyInfo.introduction: Cng ty C phn Vinafreight, c tin thn lX nghip Dch v Kho vn,c thnh lp vo nm 2001. Cng ty tp trung ch yu vo lnh vc kinh doanh cc dch v vn ti hng khng v hng hi. Vinafreight l mt trong nhng cng ty vn ti hng khng ln nht khu vc thnh ph H Ch Minh, ng th hai trong xp hng ca SingaporeAirline v th ba theo xp hng ca MalaysiaAirline v China International.Hin cng ty l thnh vin ca FIATA, IATA, VLA.Cng ty ang l i tc ca cc nh cung cp dch v vn ti hng khng, ng bin ln trn th gii nh: Singapore Airlines, Vietnam Airlines, Eva Airways, Cathay Pacific Airways, AirFrance, Bristish Airways, Philippines Airways, Lufthansa German Airlines, China Airlines, NYK Line, CMA, Maerskvi cc i th cnh tranh chnh nh Gemadept, Vitranschart, Samtra, Saigonship. Ngoi dch v vn ti, VNF cn cung cp dch v kho bi vih thng kho CFS din tch 3.000 m2, kho lnh din tch 1.500m2 sc cha khong 1800 tn;Kho ngoi tri rng10.000 m2; kho trong nh din tch6.000m2.
companyInfo.notes:
- u thp nin 90: Vinafreight l n v chuyn v vn ti hng khng c thnh lp.

- Nm 2001: B trng B Thng mi ban hnh Quyt nh s 0964/2001/Q/BTM ph duyt phng n CPH chuyn x nghip dch v kho vn thnh CTCP Vn Ti Ngoi thng, vi VL ban u l 18 t ng.

- Nm 2002: Cng ty chnh thc tr thnh thnh vin ca VIFFAS.

- Nm 2005: Cng ty tng vn iu l ln 27 t.

- Nm 2007: Cng ty tng vn iu l ln 56 t ng.

- Nm 2010: C phiu ca cng ty chnh thc c giao dch trn HNX.

- Ngy 19/05/2014: CTCP Vn Ti Ngoi Thng chnh thc i tn thnh CTCP Vinafreight theo GCNKD thay i ln th 7 ngy 19/05/2014 ca S KH&T TPHCM.

- Ngy 14/05/2021: Cng ty tng vn iu l ln 251.45 t ng.

- Ngy 24/12/2021: Tng vn iu l ln 264 t ng.
